quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  35,1,"Jettooje ngoodanii Alla, Tak…óo kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, ba…ó…óo Malaa'ikaaji nulaa…ďe, mar…ďe gabitanji(bibje) …ói …ói…ói, …ói tati e nayi. Homo …ďesda ko o muuyi e tagu makko ngun, tawde pellet, Alla ko kattan…óo kala hu'unde."
  35,2,"Kala yurmeende nde Alla udditani yim…ďe …ďen, jogitotoo…óo nde alaa; kala kadi ko o jogitii, gaccitoowo …óum alaa …ďaawo (jogitagol) makko. Ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, √Īee√Ī…óo."
  35,3,"Eey mon yo yim…ďe! NjaŇčtee neema Alla on e mon. Hara tagoowo ko woori Alla no woodi, mo no arsikira on ka kammu e ka leydi? Dewetee…óo alaa si wonaa KaŇčko! E ko honno njilirte…óon [e kaa goonga]?"
  35,4,"Si …ďe njeddii i ma, pellet Nulaa…ďe (goo) yeddanooma ado maa. Ko fa'ade e Alla, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin."
  35,5,"Eey mon yo yim…ďe! Ngandee pellet fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wota nguurndam aduna hodu on, wota (seytaane) kodoowo on hod on e fii Alla."
  35,6,"Pellet, seytaane ko ga√Īo wonani on. Haray njogitoree mo ga√Īo. Nganndee ko o noddirta fedde makko nden, ko no …ďe jeydiree e yim…ďe dul…ďoowe ngen."
  35,7,"Hino woodani yeddu…ďe …ďen, lepte ca…ótu…óe. ∆Āeya gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, hino woodani …ďe haforaneede e njo…ďdi mawndi."
  35,8,"E ko on cu…óinanaa…óo golle mum bon…óe, hara himo yi'a …óe mo∆ī∆īu…óe? - Tawde pellet, Alla no majjina on mo o muuyi, O feewna mo o muuyi. Wota a tampinir hoore-maa, sunagol fii ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, Alla ko ganndu…óo ko …ďe ngoni gollude."
  35,9,"Ko Alla woni gurtu…óo keneeli …óin, …ói cogga duule, Min njarnira …óum leydi yo'orundi; Min nguurnitira …óum leydi ndin, …ďaawo ndi yo'orude. Ko wano non ummital ngal."
  35,10,"Kala taw…óo ko teddungal faalaa (yo o …óa…ď…ďir Alla), tawde ko Alla jeyi teddungal ngal fof: ko ka makko woni ko konngol laa…ďungol ∆īawata, golle mo∆ī∆īe …óen …ďamta ngol. ∆Āeen fewjoo…ďe boneeji, hino woodani …ďe lepte ca…ótu…óe. Pewje …ďen …óen, ko bonat …óe."
  35,11,"Ko Alla tagiri on e mbulbuldi, refti e to…ď…ďere (maniiyu), refti o wa…ói on nooneeji. Deyel caawataa, ngel leelnataa kadi, si wonaa e anndal makko. Guurnaa…óo wuurnetaake, …óuytetaake kadi e nguurndam makko, si wonaa no e deftere. Pellet, …óuum ko newanii …óum Alla."
  35,12,"Maaje …óen …ói…ói potataa: [Ndiyam] goo …óoo …óam, ko mbel…óam, laa…ďungo, newiingo njaram mum, ngoo …óaa, ko lam…óam kaa…óu…óam. Hi…óon √Īaama e kala majjam, teewu keccu, ho…óon njaltina kadi hern, cu…óaari ndi …ďoornoto…óon. Hi…óa yi'a laa…óe …óen no awja e maggo, fii yo on …óa…ď…ďiron e …ďural Makko. Mbelejo'o on njettay [Mo]."
  35,13,"Himo naanta jemma on e deer √Īalawma on, O naatna √Īalawma on e ndeer jemma on. O eleti kadi na'ange ngen e lewru ndun. Kala mun no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Ko On moo…óon woni Alla, Joomi mon: Ko KaŇčko Laamu woodani. ∆äiya …ói noddoton ga makko, …ói jeytaa yeru gorol tamara."
  35,14,"Si on noddu …ói, …ói nanataa noddaandu mon; hay si …ói nanoy, …ói njaabitotaako on. √Ďande Darngal, …ói njeddoyat sirku mon on. Alaa kabroowo ma, wano kumpitii…óo On."
  35,15,"Eey mon yo yim…ďe, ko onon ngoni hatonjim…ďe e Alla …ďen, Alla kan, ko KaŇčko woni Galo jettinii…óo On."
  35,16,"Si O yi…óii, o na…ďa on, o adda tagu hesu."
  35,17,"∆äuum wonaani cattu…óum to Alla."
  35,18,"WoŇčki ronndotaako doŇčgal woŇčkii goo. Hay si teddiraaki [junuubi] kin noddii e ronndaneede, ki ronndantaake hay hu'unde, hay si ko …ďadondiraa…óo Anndu ko jeertintaa [nana waaju], ko …ďen huliroo…ďe Joomi mum ka wirnii, …ďe √Īii…ďi e Juulde. Kala on la…ď…ďinii…óo, haray ko hoore makko o woni la…ď…ďinanaade. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde nden."
  35,19,"Bum…óo e ji'oowo potataa,"
  35,20,"wonaa ni…ďe …óen e ndaygu ngun,"
  35,21,"wonaa …óowdi ndi e henndu wulndu ndu."
  35,22,"Wonaa kadi wuur…ďe …ďen potata e maay…ďe …ďen. Pellet, Alla no nanina on mo o muuyani. Wanaa an [Nulaa…óo], woni naninoowo, won…ďe ka genaale …ďeen."
  35,23,"Aan a wonaani, si wonaa jerrtinoowo."
  35,24,"Pellet, Min nulirii ma goonga, ko a beltinoowo e jeertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wonaa jerrtinoowo fe∆ī∆īii e ma…ď…ďe."
  35,25,"Si …ďe njeddii ma, hari adinoo…ďe …ďe …ďen njedduno (Nulaa…ďe mum), feewndo …ďen Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe ngaddannoo …ďanngannduyeeji, e ∆äeri e feftere ndayginoore."
  35,26,"Refti nanngitir mi yeddu…ďe …ďen (halakuyee). Tesko no lepte am …óen mba…ótinirnoo."
  35,27,"E a yiaani won'de Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Min pu…óiniri …óam dim…óe ceertu…óe noone. Hino ka pelle, …óate daneeje e bo…óeeje ceertyu…óe noone, e pete …ďaleeje."
  35,28,"Hino e yim…ďe …ďen, e daabeeji …óin, e neemoraa…ói …óin, …ói nooneeji mum kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko kulata Alla e jiyaa…ďe makko …ďeen, ko anndu…ďe …ďen. Pellet, Alla ko poolu…óo, kaforoowo."
  35,29,"∆Āeen janngoo…ďe deftere Alla nden, …ďe √Īii…ďi e Juulde, …ďe nafqii ko Min arsiki …ďe kon gunndoo e kene, he…ďe njoortii njulaaku ngu sontataa."
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana …ďe njo…ďdiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, o …ďeyda …ďe e …ďural makko ngal. KaŇčko, ko o kaforoowo, gannditanoowo [on] ."
  35,31,"Kon ko Min wahayini e maa…óa e deftere nden, ko …óuum woni goonga, gooŇč…óinde e …óen won'…óe ye'eso mayre. Pellet, Alla ko kumpitii…óo deentu…óo jiyaa…ďe makko …ďen."
  35,32,"Refti Min ndonini deftere nden, …ďen …ďe Min cu…ďii e jiyaa…ďe Amen. Hino e ma…ď…ďe too√Ī…ďe hoore-mun, mum hino e ma…ď…ďe hakindin…óo, hino e ma…ď…ďe foolondiroo…ďe e mo∆ī∆īereeji, duŇčayee Alla; ko …óum woni …ďural mawnungal ngal."
  35,33,"Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, …ói naatata e mum, hara he…ďe cu…óiree ton, jawe kaŇčŇče e kaalise e lu‚Äôu-lu‚Äôu; comci ma…ď…ďe …óin ton, ko cooyi."
  35,34,"∆Āe mbi'a: ""jettooje Ngoodanii Alla, On ittan…óo en suno. Pellet, Joomi men, ko kaforoowo, barjotoo…óo."
  35,35,"On jippinir…óo en …ďural makko ngal, e galle √Īii…ďal, tampere (woo) he…ďataa en ton, wonaa roŇčkere ke…ďata en ton."
  35,36,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen kan, ko Yiite Jahannama woodani …ďen; maayde √Īaawetaake e ma…ď…ďe, sakko …ďe maaya, …ďe koynantaake kadi lepte magge …óen. Ko wano nii Min njo…ďitirta kala jeddu…óo."
  35,37,"Hara he…ďe ooloo nder ton […ďe mbi'a]: ""Joomi amen, yaltin min; min ngolla mo∆ī∆īere, hara wonah ko min ngollatnoo kon"". [O jaaboo …ďe]: ""E min wuurnaano on yeru ko waajitotoo…óo waajitoranoo e mum? Jeertinoowo kadi ari e mon? Awa mee…óee, sabu faabo alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen""."
  35,38,"Pellet, Alla ko ganndu…óo wirnii…ói kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin. Ko O ganndu…óo ko suu…óii e …ďer…óe."
  35,39,"Ko KaŇčko woni ba…óu…óo on lomtii…ďe ka leydi. Kala jeddu…óo, ko e makko lorra jeddi makko yantata. Jeddugol he'efer…ďe …ďen, …ďeydataa …ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa tikkere. Jeddugol …ďeydataa heefer…ďe …ďen, si wanaa hayrere."
  35,40,"Maaku: ""E on nji'ii rendii…ói mon ndewoton ga Alla …óin? Kollee Kam ko …ói tagi ka leydi. Kaa hi…ói mari ge…óal e [tagugol] kammuuji …óin? Kaa Min addan …ďe deftere, nde …ďe woni e …ďanndannduyee mum? Si ko woni, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen alaa e fodude yoga ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa hodo""."
  35,41,"Pellet, ko Alla jogitii kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, fii wata …ói dirtu. Hay si …ói ndirtayno, hay gooto jogitotaako …ói e …ďaawo makko. O laatike mu√Ī√Īii…óo, kaforoowo."
  35,42,"∆Āe ngoodndiri Alla, hattirde e goondooje ma…ď…ďe, won'de si jeertinoowo arii e ma…ď…ďe, pellet, …ďe ngonay …ďur…ďe feewude wootere e mofte …óen. Nde jeertinoowo non arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, …óum …ďeydaali …ďe, si wonaa wo…ó…óitagol."
  35,43,"[∆Āe mba…óiri …óum] mawnintinaare ka keydi, e pewje …ďen…óe. Pewje bon…óe …óen non kuu…ďitataa, si wonaa jom-munm en. Hara hi…ďe cabbitii, si wonaa sunna (Alla) on e adinoo…ďe …ďen? A he…ďantaa sunna Alla on battiigu, a he…ďantaa sunna Alla mbaylir…óum."
  35,44,"E …ďee njiilaaki ka leydi, …ďe taskoo ko holno battane adinoo…ďe …ďen wonirnoo? Hari no …ďuri …ďe tii…óude doole. Alla siforaali won'de go…ó…óum no roŇčkina Mo ka kammuuji maa ka leydi. Tawde pellet, ko O ganndu…óo, kattan…óo."
  35,45,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yim…ďe …ďen ko …ďe paggitorii kon, o accataano ruugayngel e dow mayri. Ko woni tan, Homo nee…ďnitana …ďe haa e lajal anndaa ngal. Si lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal heewtii, [O nanngay …ďe], tawde pellet, Alla ko deenu…óo jiyaa…ďe makko …ďen."
